Authors:
Vanessa Scheffenacker, Joseph Strauss, Harald Berger,
Christian Voitl, Hazal Kandemir, Alena Kubátová, Roman Labuda
Title:
Gymnascella wieselburgensis (Gymnoascaceae), sp. nov., a new
onygenalean fungus from Austria
Abstract:
A new Gymnascella species was described from a sample of
dust obtained from a cow wall. Morphological descriptions of the isolate
and the results of phylogenetic analyses were provided.
